                <p>
                    <bold>
                        <italic>Recent Advances in Cardiovascular Drug Discovery</italic>
                    </bold> publishes review and research articles, drug clinical trial studies and guest edited thematic issues on cardiovascular drug discovery.  The scope covers but is not limited to,  medicinal chemistry, pharmacology, genomics, biochemistry, novel bioactive compounds, analogs &#x0026; targets,  and important patents in cardiovascular drug discovery research.</p>
