            <journal-description>The journal is essential reading for all researchers involved in cardiovascular drug design and discovery. The journal also covers recent research (where patents have been registered) in fast emerging therapeutic areas/targets &amp; therapeutic agents related to cardiovascular drug discovery.</journal-description>
